
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <meta name="description" content="">
    <meta name="author" content="">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="../../assets/ico/favicon.ico">

    <title>Sign Into Chawk Server</title>


	<!-- Core CSS - Include with every page -->
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "narrow_jumbotron", media: "all", "data-turbolinks-track" => true %>
	<%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  </head>

  <body>

    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <ul class="nav nav-pills pull-right">
          <li class="active"><a href="/">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about.html">About</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact.html">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
        <h3 class="text-muted">Queuetue's Chawk Server</h3>
      </div>

        <div id="page-wrapper">
            <div class="col-lg-12">
				<% flash.each do |type, message| %>
	            <div class="alert alert-success alert-dismissable">
	                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button>
	                <%= message %>
	            </div>
	            <% end %>
        	</div>
    		<%= yield %>
       </div>

      <div class="jumbotron">
      	<%= image_tag "Jackdaw.svg" %>
      	<hr style=" border-color: #EEEEEE -moz-use-text-color #FFFFFF;border-style: solid none;border-width: 1px 0;margin: 18px 0;"/>
        <p class="lead">This is a Chawk server.  Chawk is an engine that lets you store little pieces of data and sort, display and aggregate them together to make more sense out of them. </p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-success" href="<%=  user_omniauth_authorize_path(:google_oauth2)  %>" role="button">Sign in wth Google</a></p>
        <p style="text-align: justify; font-size:1em"><small>This is a <strong style="color:#990000">TEST SERVER</strong>.  Any data placed on this server may be deleted at any time.  Your data will not be shared with anyone for any nefarious or marketing purposes - but this is early alpha software, so keep anything private to yourself!</small></p>
      </div>

      <div class="row marketing">
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <h4>Track your Greenhouse.</h4>
          <p>Your green thumb can get that much greener if you know what's going on - and you can look back on it to help yourself improve, or use it to share with others anywhere in the world.</p>


          <h4>Compare Sales and Revenue.</h4>
          <p>Tie together data in ways that use dot require a half-dozen spreadsheets, ad discovernew insights about how your business runs.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <h4>Know your Impact.</h4>
          <p>Everyone wants to save on fuel costs and reduce impact on the environment.  Chawk can let you store data directly from your car - and compare it to weather conditions, traffic, fuel prices and any other data - years later.</p>

          <h4>Give your Technology a Voice.</h4>
          <p>More and more gadgets, excercise gear, toys and appliances are starting to have something to say - but who will listen?  Chawk lets you store that data and collate it later when you want big answers.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Learn more about Chawk at <a href="http://github.com/queuetue/chawk-server">Github</a></p>
      </div>

    </div> <!-- /container -->
  </body>
</html>
